tory since Tokyo 2020,\\\" the body charged with organizing the sports extravaganza in the \\\"City of Love\\\" said in a statement to Reuters.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999626411415, \"rank\": 3.732879669708138e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports extravaganza\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"Love\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But for Paris 2024 the choice of these beds for the Olympic and Paralympic Village is primarily linked to a wider ambition to ensure minimal environmental impact and a second life for all equipment used during the short period of the Games.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9976123272564121, \"rank\": 0.0023933873694262273, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_